the eclipse will occur all times are eastern daylight 
moon enters penumbra 823 pm 
moon enters umbra 921 pm 
moon enters totality 1020 pm 
middle of eclipse 1108 pm 
moon leaves totality 1156 pm 
moon leaves umbra 1256 am thursday 
moon leaves penumbra 153 am 
