highly principled dedicated hardworking public servants who are 
genuinely interested in serving the public good 
leland was one of them although not all of his colleagues or his 
constituents were captivated by his driving humanitarianism he was 
sometimes criticized for his obsession with bringing relief to the 
starving people of africa his detractors said he should have 
concentrated on the hungry people of the united states instead 
but leland had an answer for that i am as much a citizen of 
this world as i am of my country he said to hell with those 
people who are critical of what i am able to do to help save 
peoples lives i dont mean to sound hokey but i grew up on a 
christian ethic which says we are supposed to help the least of our 
brothers 
</TEXT>
