camp outside the west german consulate tuesday and moved to a nearby 
roman catholic church 
a crush of passport and asylum requests by east germans has 
overwhelmed west german diplomats in this city and east berlin the 
embassy and consulate were closed in budapest monday and the west 
german mission shut down in east berlin on aug 8 
