different from what was being proposed at homewoodflossmoor 
in that case there was credible evidence that the athletes had 
a serious drug problem he said 
he also called the suburban schools expanded plan the first step 
down the wrong road 
anything that erodes societys expectations of privacy for 
students i think is trouble he said 
