this year and clark is considering staying open yearround instead 
of closing in the winter months 
i found out after i became acquainted with branson that 
everyone else in life knew about it but me clark said i run 
into people in almost every state who say they plan branson every 
year as part of their vacation 
branson has a population of 2500 but on a typical summer day 
