<TEXT>
home shopping network inc pitches 
cookware and jewelry to millions of tv viewers but the video 
retailers more important audience is a judge who will rule on its 
appeal of a 100 million libel award 
the financially ailing company which could be devastated by such 
a large forfeiture is seeking to reverse or reduce the jury award 
granted gte corp earlier this month 
in an earlier lawsuit of its own hsn had accused gte of 
installing an inadequate telephone system at the retailers 
clearwater headquarters which it blamed for missed calls from 
viewers and the loss of millions of dollars worth of sales 
but the case boomeranged on hsn when gte successfully 
countersued claiming that its reputation was smeared by hsns 
accusations which it called false 
the hsn appeal awaiting state circuit judge howard rives when he 
returns from vacation later this month alleges 336 faults in the 
sixweek case ranging from improper evidence to rives demeanor 
described as grumpy 
the aug 2 verdict was grossly excessive and was the product of 
prejudice passion and gross confusion said hsn in its appeal 
motions filed monday 
much of the appeal focuses on rives decision to permit gtes 
libel counterclaim to be heard in the same trial as the 15 billion 
hsn suit rives also is accused of prejudicing jurors against hsn 
and its attorneys 
gte spokeswoman jan morris declined to comment on the motions 
but said the stamford connbased telecommunications giant would 
answer the challenges in court 
a hearing on the appeal before rives has been set for nov 28 
this promises to go on for months said hsn spokewoman kathy 
jurado we said all along well try to get this overturned 
nonetheless some people familiar with the case speculate that 
gte may be interested in settling the matter by working out a lower 
settlement with hsn which claimed it lost 500 million in sales 
when gtes telephone system could not handle an increasing volume of 
calls in 1986 and 1987 
