louis marckesano an analyst with janney montgomery scott inc 
said a deal involving ual management and its employees would 
eliminate fears in congress and the department of transportation 
that the airline would be stripped of valuable assets as might 
happen with a leveraged buyout 
a leveraged buyout is an acquisition financed mainly by borrowed 
funds that are repaid with the target companys cash flow or the 
