gaming analysts believe resorts 
international inc will have to make a dramatic move to pull out of 
its financial slump 
on tuesday one day after resorts posted a large secondquarter 
loss the conclusions were near unanimous 
they have got to recapitalize in some way shape or form 
said saul leonard a los angelesbased analyst with laventhol amp 
horwath 
with two gaming halls selling one might be a very viable 
alternative he said 
